BASE_URL = "https://www.i.ua/"
USER_NAME = Examtester123
USER_PASSWORD = 123456qwerty

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
TestCase #001 - Test Case to verify the functionality of the Login Page

Preconditions:
1. Open the browser [optional]
2. Check user USER_NAME exist in the system and if not create a new user with NEW_USER_NAME and USER_PASSWORD

Steps:
1. Open the browser [optional]
2. Navigate to the BASE_URL
3. Enter the username  USER_NAME
4. Enter the password  USER_PASSWORD
5. Click on the Sign In button

Expected Result:
6. Verify user sees the Home Page (sees button "My profile" and does not see button "Sign In")

Postconditions:
1. Delete user USER_NAME from the system

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

TestCase #002 - Test Case to verify validation messages  on the Login Page when user enters invalid data

Preconditions:
1. Open the browser [optional]
2. Check user USER_NAME exist in the system and if not create a new user with NEW_USER_NAME and USER_PASSWORD

Steps:
1. Open the browser [optional]
2. Navigate to the BASE_URL
3. Enter the username   {"Examtester123"} or {"Exam"},
4. Enter the password   {"tr"} or {"123456qwerty"},
3. Click on the Sign In button

Expected Result:
4. Verify user sees the validation message "Invalid username/password" and does not see button "My profile"

Postconditions:
1. Delete user USER_NAME from the system

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

TestCase #003 - Test Case to verify exchange rate on the Exchange Page

Preconditions:
1. Open the browser [optional]

Steps:
1. Open Exchange Rate Page
2. Enter the amount 100
3. Select currency USD
4. Click on the button "Calculate"

Expected Result:
5. Verify user sees the result of the calculation



