TestCase #004 - Test Case to verify sending email

Preconditions:
1. Open the browser [optional]
2. Check user USER_NAME exist in the system and if not create a new user with NEW_USER_NAME and USER_PASSWORD

Steps:

1. check that user is logged in
2. click on the button "New message"
3. enter the email address USER_EMAIL
4. enter the subject "Test"
5. enter the text "Test"
6. click on the button "Send"

Expected Result:
7. Verify user sees the message "Лист успішно відправлено адресатам"
8. Check sent email in the Sent folder

Postconditions:
1. Delete user USER_NAME from the system

